    <item>
      <title>奥尔班要求特朗普时间表 俄罗斯制裁可能失效</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/orban-risks-russia-sanctions-lapse-with-demand-on-trump-timeline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班告诉欧盟领导人，他希望等到他的盟友唐纳德·特朗普就职后再决定是否延长欧盟对俄罗斯的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/orban-risks-russia-sanctions-lapse-with-demand-on-trump-timeline</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 20:39:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国央行行长呼吁大幅削减赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/france-s-central-bank-chief-calls-for-significant-deficit-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国央行行长弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦德加洛表示，新政府明年仍必须以大幅削减赤字为目标，尽管这种努力导致了上届政府的垮台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/france-s-central-bank-chief-calls-for-significant-deficit-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 19:57:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CFTC 面临资金耗尽的风险，无法向举报人支付佣金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/cftc-risks-running-out-of-money-to-pay-whistleblowers-their-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国衍生品市场监管机构去年创纪录地投入了 171 亿美元打击涉嫌欺诈和市场操纵者，但现在它可能会成为自身成功的牺牲品，因为它希望奖励那些提供帮助的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/cftc-risks-running-out-of-money-to-pay-whistleblowers-their-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 19:46:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降低降息预期后市政债券暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/munis-plummet-after-fed-dials-back-expectations-for-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔对 2025 年降息持更为谨慎的看法后，市政债券出现数周来最大跌幅，这令投资者震惊，并导致全球债券市场崩溃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/munis-plummet-after-fed-dials-back-expectations-for-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 19:29:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>预计 2025 年写字楼市场将反弹，而其他房地产股将陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/real-estate-stocks-to-split-in-2025-as-offices-beat-homebuilders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自美联储于 2022 年开始加息以来，房地产股经历了充满挑战的几年，借贷成本飙升，房地产市场崩溃。尽管 2024 年中期出现了健康反弹，但 2025 年的前景并不特别令人乐观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/real-estate-stocks-to-split-in-2025-as-offices-beat-homebuilders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 16:35:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息后，美国收益率曲线创 2022 年以来最陡峭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/us-yield-curve-is-steepest-since-2022-after-fed-s-rate-cut-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[较长期美国国债周四走弱，推动收益率曲线趋陡至大约 30 个月前的水平，此前美联储采取了强硬的利率放松政策，并预计明年降息次数将减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/us-yield-curve-is-steepest-since-2022-after-fed-s-rate-cut-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 15:27:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
